author: Natalie Neil
title: Natalie Neil
text: Love tails, great food, easy to use on the web updating our pups details , great delivery, delivered to our door each month by the fantastic delivery company Yodel but more importantly our dog Ted loves Tails he is a thriving pup and has an amazing glossy coat that everyone comments on. Highly recommend and do glad my friend recommended Tails.com to me when we got our new edition. Ted 🐶💙😍😊Xxxx
